Package com.zhuinden.simplestack.navigator

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DefaultStateChanger.StatePersistenceStrategy
    Allows replacing the default Navigator-based view state persistence with a custom one.
    DefaultStateChanger.ViewChangeCompletionListener
    Allows the possibility of listening to when the view change is completed.
    DefaultStateChanger.ViewChangeCompletionListener.Callback
    Notifies the DefaultStateChanger that the view change completion listener completed its callback.
    StateKey
    This must be implemented to represent state using DefaultStateChanger.
    ViewChangeHandler
    An interface that represents the view change when a state change occurs.
    ViewChangeHandler.CompletionCallback
    It must be called to signal that the view change is complete.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BackstackHost
    This is public because it has to be.
    DefaultStateChanger
    A default state changer that handles view changes, and allows an optional external state changer (which is executed before the view change).
    DefaultStateChanger.Configurer
    Used to configure the instance of the DefaultStateChanger.
    Navigator
    Convenience class to hide lifecycle integration using retained fragment.
    Navigator.Installer
    A configurer for Navigator.
